text: La Mosca Tsé – Tsé or simply La Mosca (in English: "The Tsetse Fly") is an Argentine rock fusion band. Thier music was generally ska, cumbia, merengue, salsa and pop rock.Biografía de La Mosca Retrieved December 20, 2015 The group was formed in 1995.Biography of La Mosca Retrieved December 20, 2015 ==References== Category:Argentine musicians
